nodes.text: Star Wars: Bounty Hunters: Galaxy's Deadliest

Star Wars: Bounty Hunters: Galaxy's Deadliest is the first story arc of Marvel Comics' ongoing series Star Wars: Bounty Hunters. The arc comprises the first five issues of the series, and was written by Ethan Sacks, with art by Paolo Villanelli.
